*[[AFI's 100 Years...100 Laughs]] (#20),&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web |title=AFI's 100 Years...100 Laughs |url=http://www.afi.com/Docs/100Years/laughs100.pdf |publisher=[[American Film Institute]] |accessdate=2016-07-17}}&lt;/ref&gt;
